title: Author Justin St. Germain to read at Oregon State University (Oregon State University)
text: ( Source : Oregon State University ) CORVALLIS, Ore. - Author Justin St. Germain , a new faculty member at Oregon State University, will read from his work at 7:30 p.m. on Friday, Oct. 16. The reading will be in the Valley Library Rotunda , 201
